data.description: Welcome to 8123 Ashwood Pointe, a charming single-story home nestled in the sought-after Northwest side of San Antonio, Texas. This residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience in a desirable neighborhood. This home's single-story layout ensures ease of living with all your essential spaces on one level, making it an ideal choice for individuals and families alike. Featuring 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 well-appointed bathrooms, this home provides ample private space for the whole family. The entire home is adorned with ceramic tile flooring, not only enhancing the aesthetics but also ensuring easy maintenance. The open floorplan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an inviting and spacious living environment. It's perfect for hosting gatherings, family dinners, or simply relaxing. The well-equipped kitchen boasts modern amenities, making meal preparation a pleasure. With ample counter space and cabinetry, it's a functional and stylish focal point of the home. Step outside to discover your private outdoor retreat, where you can bask in the Texan sun, entertain guests, or create your own oasis. Located by loads of shopping, dining, and other entertainment. Make this your home today!
